    <div class="mx-auto max-w-7xl px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-16 text-left">
      <h2 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-semibold text-[#111827]">
        Our service covers everything from the big picture to the <span
          class="text-[#5271FF]">smallest details</span
        >
      </h2>
      <p class="mt-3 text-[#111827]/80">
        With over 8 years of experience recruiting in Sri Lanka, we've built
        unmatched expertise in the local talent market. Our deep understanding
        of Sri Lankan work culture and professional standards ensures we match
        you with highly skilled candidates who align perfectly with your
        requirements.
      </p>
    </div>
